%% Graph 2: Layered Context Architecture -- Three layers of context with enterprise examples

flowchart LR
    subgraph Global["🌐 Global Layer — permanent"]
        direction LR
        G1["🏢 Company identity & values"]
        G2["📏 Coding standards & policies"]
        G3["🎨 Tone, style, compliance rules"]
    end

    subgraph Project["📁 Project Layer — project lifetime"]
        direction LR
        P1["🎯 Project goals & status"]
        P2["📊 Domain knowledge & research"]
        P3["👥 Stakeholders & decisions"]
    end

    subgraph Task["⚡ Task Layer — per session"]
        direction LR
        T1["📄 Current documents & data"]
        T2["🔧 Active tools & APIs"]
        T3["💬 Conversation history"]
    end

    Global --> Project --> Task

    Task --> LLM["🤖 LLM Context Window"]

    style Global fill:#e8f4fd,stroke:#2980b9,color:#333
    style Project fill:#fef9e7,stroke:#f39c12,color:#333
    style Task fill:#fdedec,stroke:#e74c3c,color:#333
    style LLM fill:#eafaf1,stroke:#27ae60,color:#333,stroke-width:3px
